task.summary: Adding some API routes and controllers (some for SKU, some for Assets). Short script with mongodb manual data population. Moved models to /app_api dir.
Added API get controllers for mfg, locations, groups and health status.
Add POST, PUT and DELETE for SKU, Mfg and Locations.
Add POST, PUT and DELETE for group and health status, start for hw_model.
Add POST, PUT and DELETE for hw_model.
Add GET, POST, PUT and DELETE for assets.
Add API requests to frontend, beginning.
Asset details now through API request. Added generic-text.jade and _showError utility. Fix a typo in layout.jade
Add list views for skus, manufacturers, locations, groups and hstats.
SKU and manufacturers now have separate server controllers, added add and delete features for each. Also added jade template for item add form.
Locations, groups and health stats now have separate server controllers. Added item info for all admin categories, as well as jade template for it. Fix link in item-admin.jade.
Add addAsset function, using async to get skus, mfgs, etc. Add template for add asset form.
